{"tid":2426454,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★老翁心悸與接種疫苗無關！接種中心總監：\"是接種疫苗後發生\"","createTime":"2021-02-28T06:07:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T14:19:48.000Z","uid":19454,"like":74,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"fcd97d39032617191fbc315959280200f6dd2238","tid":2426454,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T06:07:49.000Z","msg":"<strong>接種中心承辦商相信老翁心悸與接種疫苗無關</strong><br />\n<br />\n官涌體育館疫苗接種中心醫務總監郭寶賢：「<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>這件事是接種疫苗後發生</strong></span>，也是較短時間，這位病人未曾試過心律不齊的情況，所以是新發現，我們安全起見把他送院，作為安全措施。以我認識不大關係，接種疫苗短時間內，此情況發生，又不是血液（靜脈）注射，他的反應不應是這樣，疫苗注射最擔心是過敏反應。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=425613\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425613&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3gzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=0329e862\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425613&h=7671761b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=425613</a>"},{"pid":"ff52bf15dc687d97873833b314eca034874c9884","tid":2426454,"uid":19454,"like":98,"dislike":0,"score":98,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T06:08:41.000Z","msg":"唔通接種前發生咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51b5a6d0b6c2e7ffe0c90eb06ca8a239d72eb2f","tid":2426454,"uid":24730,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T06:10:48.000Z","msg":"都話咗死咗都唔會賠錢畀你，一定同疫苗無關"},{"pid":"cb4ad80f1c809d5de8b8e2128aa625f0de02fec5","tid":2426454,"uid":19454,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T06:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oZ75d6G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi